ic and global companies financial products our portfolio of financing products and trustee services financial services monetary settlement asset management and foreign exchange offerings custody services a valuable partnership when you invest in the japanese securities market yen clearing services offering various clearing  settlement services globally global business mizuho has rich experience in overseas markets an extensive international group network and a cuttingedge range of financial products it is a top of the sub menu branchesjapan overseas offices home products  services closehome branchesjapan overseas offices products  services markets  reports about mizuho bank careers japanese site map pc site top close top of page mizuho financial group inc mfg company profile  reuterscom x edition united states africa américa latina عربي argentina brasil canada  deutschland españa france india italia  méxico россия united kingdom united states profile mizuho financial group inc mfg related topics stocksstock screenerfinancialsbanks overview news key developments people charts financials analysts research pulse mfg on new york consolidated usd  jul  change  chg   prev close  open  days high  days low  volume  avg vol  wk high  wk low  full description mizuho financial group inc mhfg incorporated on january   is a financial holding company the company through its subsidiaries provides domestic and international financial services in japan and other countries the companys segments include mhbk mhtb mhsc and others the mhbk segment includes personal banking retail banking corporate banking large corporations corporate banking financial institutions  public sector business international banking and trading and others the mhtb segment provides products and services related to trust real estate securitization and structured finance pension and asset management and stock transfers the mhsc segment provides securities services to corporations financial institutions public sector entities and individuals its others segment consists of mhfg its subsidiaries other than mizuho bank ltd mhbk mizuho trust  banking co ltd mhtb and mizuho securities co ltd mhsc and its equitymethod affiliates they provide a range of customers with their various products and services such as those related to trust and custody asset management and private banking through companies such as trust  custody services bank ltd tcsb mizuho asset management co ltd diam co ltd an equitymethod affiliate and mizuho private wealth management co ltd the others segment also provides nonbanking services including research and consulting services through mizuho research institute ltd and information technologyrelated services through mizuho information  research institute incthe personal banking segment provides financial products and services such as housing loans deposits investment trusts and individual insurance to individual customers through mhbks nationwide branches and automated teller machine atm network as well as telephone and internet banking services in addition the personal banking segment handles trust products as an agent of mhtb the retail banking segment provides financial products and services such as consulting services of business succession and asset inheritance and asset management for business owners and highnetworth customers the retail banking segment also provides overall banking services for small and medium enterprises smes the corporate banking large corporations segment provides a range of financial solutions on a global basis to large japanese corporations and their affiliates by integrating the companys specialty functions including banking trust and securities based on relationships with mhbks domestic customers and by utilizing its global industry knowledgethe corporate banking segment provides to larger smes financial products and services the corporate banking segment also provides solutions to customers financial needs such as stable fundraising mergers and acquisitions management buyout business succession entry into new business and business restructuring for customers in mature or transition stages the financial institutions  public sector business segment provides advisory services and solutions such as advice on financial strategy and risk management to financial institutions and provides financial products and services that include funding support via the subscription and underwriting of bonds to public sector entities the international banking segment offers products such as project finance and trade finance for overseas customers the trading and others segment provides derivatives and other risk hedging products to satisfy mhbks customers financial and business risk control requirements the trading and others is also engaged in mhbks trading such as foreign exchange and bond trading and asset and liability management its inhouse companies include the retail  business banking company the corporate  institutional company the global corporate company the global markets company and the asset management companyretail  business banking companythe company provides services such as inheritance distribution service and testamentarytrust that utilize trust function and it has expanded its line of products such as family trusts and annual fund giving trusts with respect to the loan business it offers various products and services in response to each customers life stage including release of products utilizing value of housing assets of the customer it also provides productsservices with officers and directors of its corporate clients such as opening account for payrolls providing housing loans and management of retirement payments among others as of march   it had expanded its branch network throughout japan mizuho bank  mizuho trust  banking  mizuho securities  and its atm network approximately  locations including atms shared with aeon bank as of march   it also had  of mizuho securities planet booths which are located in the branches and offices of mizuho bank and  of mizuho trust  banking trust lounges which are located in the branches and offices of mizuho bank it offers multilayered solutions in response to the various development stages of its customers businesses it offers optimal solutions for businesses such as offering syndicated loans targeted at small and mediumsized enterprises and middle market firms advisory services related to overseas expansions mergers and acquisitionsrelated services and business matching services in addition to developing the financial products brokerage business and managing the initiatives to manage the customer base for trustee business for defined contribution pension planscorporate  institutional companythe corporate  institutional company engages in relationship management for its customers that are large corporations financial institutions and public sector businesses in japan the company offers groupwide financial solutions that are tailor made for each customer such as syndicate loans and bonds on a global basis to meet its customers needs in fundraising investment management and financial strategies it provides optimal financial services groupwide that include funding support as a trustee and underwriter of public bonds and services as a designated financial institutionglobal corporate companythe global corporate company works with nonjapanese companies and japanese companies operating outside japan for its japanese corporate customers the company provides unified support both in and outside japan to help them expand their overseas operations it offers specialized services that use its advanced financial technologies and expertise particularly in the asia region it supports japanese corporate customers developing new markets by offering advisory and other services it is also working with governmentaffiliated institutions and financial institutions of various countries forming business alliances as necessary to provide uptodate local information and other entry support to its customers interested in starting business in new marketsglobal markets companyin addition to asset liability management and investment business with respect to interest rates equities and credit among others the global markets company focuses to provide sales and trading services to a range of customers from individuals to institutional investors by offering a range of market related products such as interest rates foreign exchange equities and commodities with respect to the sales and trading business through a management structure based on customer segments the company offers detailed products and services to meet the diverse needs of its customers and support their global business by integrating its banking trust and securities functions and utilizing its global networkasset management companythe asset management company develops products and provides services that correspond to the needs of a range of customer base ranging from individuals to institutional investors in the alternative investment business it provides its customers with products by collaborating with its group companies including mizuho alternative investments llc in the united states mizuho global alternative investments ltd in tokyo which selects and introduces hedge funds and eurekahedge pte ltd in singapore which is its subsidiary providing hedge fund research and data services in addition it develops global financial products by collaborating with blackrock inc and arranges and offers products related to private equity and infrastructure funds by collaborating with partner group agthe company competes with mitsubishi ufj financial group sumitomo mitsui financial group japan finance corporation japan post bank development bank of japan and japan bank for international cooperation » full overview of mfg company address mizuho financial group inc otemachi tower otemachichiyodaku   tky    p  company web links home page officers  directors 