ices including asset management and asset succession payroll services and sells lottery tickets issued by prefectures and ordinancedesignated cities in addition it offers financial solutions such as bonds mergers and acquisitions advisory etc for corporate customers to meet their needs in fundraising investment management and financial strategies solutions based on their capital management business strategy and financial strategy solutions related to real estate advisory services and solutions such as advice on financial strategy and proposals on various investment products to financial institutions and financial services that include funding support and public bonds underwriting further the company offers sales and trading services to meet risk hedging and investment needs investment products for individual customers and consulting services for institutional investors additionally the company provides products and services related to trust securitization and structured finance pension and stock transfers securities services and research private banking information technologyrelated telephone and internet banking services as of december   its branch network included  mizuho bank  mizuho trust and banking and  mizuho securities and  atms in japan the company was founded in  and is headquartered in tokyo japan detailed company description wwwmizuhofgcojp  employees last reported date  founded in  mizuho financial group inc  top compensated officers mr yasuhiro sato ceo president  representative director age  total annual compensation ¥m executives board directors compensation as of fiscal year  mizuho financial group inc mizuho financial group inc announces consolidated earnings results for the full year ended march   jul   mizuho financial group inc announced consolidated earnings results for the full year ended march   for the year the company reported total revenue was  million against  million a year ago income before income tax expense was ¥ million against ¥ mil